Package data

Class Activity

java.lang.Object
data.Activity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Activity extends Object implements Serializable
The Activity class represents an activity with a name, description, interests, start date, end date, and points given. It also contains a list of participants who are users that participate in the activity.
